About TechFocus

Leading IT Hardware Provider & Professional Services

Our Company

TechFocus, a SBA 8(a) and WOSB certified IT hardware provider, has built a strong track record of delivering exceptional service and value to our clients over the years. With over $25 million in sales, we demonstrate our commitment to customer satisfaction and solidify our position as a trusted partner in the IT hardware industry.

Government Contracts

Holding a GSA MAS contract with SIN 33411, we showcase our ability to meet stringent federal requirements and supply products to government agencies. Our certification and contract capabilities enable us to serve both commercial and government sectors effectively.

Our Solutions

As a leading provider of technology products, TechFocus has become a trusted source for IT hardware products and solutions. We offer a comprehensive range of electronic and hardware items, such as computers, monitors, peripheral products, and networking equipment, making it easy for customers to acquire the technology they need.

Our Mission

Our mission is to exceed our government customers' expectations while maintaining an unparalleled level of service in the professional services industry. We are committed to providing innovative solutions that drive success for our clients.

Why Choose TechFocus

Certified Excellence

SBA 8(a) and WOSB certified with proven track record

Government Ready

GSA MAS contract holder with SIN 33411

Proven Results

Over $25 million in successful sales and satisfied customers

Comprehensive Solutions

Full range of IT hardware and professional services
